
# --- OS / editor junk ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# --- Secrets ---
# Defensive: real .env files should never live inside this repo (only
# .env.example templates), but ignore them anyway in case one gets added.
**/.env
!**/.env.example

# --- Talon Voice ---
# Runtime cache, databases, and binary blobs
**/.talon/.sys/
# Python virtual environment
**/.talon/.venv/
# Symlinks to venv
**/.talon/bin
# Log files
**/.talon/*.log
